<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.9">
<l>koṇṭalmā rutaṅkaḷ kulavarai tokunīrk</l>
<l>kuraikaṭa lulakuṭa ṉaṉaittum</l>
<l>uṇṭamā vayiṟṟō ṉoṇcuṭa rēynta</l>
<l>vumparu mūḻiyu māṉāṉ</l>
<l>aṇṭamū ṭaṟuttaṉ ṟantarat tiḻintaṅ</l>
<l>kavaṉiyā ḷalamarap perukum</l>
<l>maṇṭumā maṇinīrk kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He whose great belly consumed the clouds, winds, mountain ranges,</l>
<l rend="indent">the roaring sea with amassed waters,</l>
<l>The world, and everything at once, he who became the eons</l>
<l rend="indent">and the heavens which befit the shining sun,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges,</l>
<l rend="indent">with surging, vast crystal waters which, splitting through the firmament</l>
<l>Then falling there through space, rose so that lady earth trembled.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
